<pb n="0009a" id="I01.0004.0009a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 4</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>韓貞等造石窟記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a01"/><p id="pI01p0009a0101">員外散騎常侍昌黎韓貞。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a02"/><note n="0009001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">葥＝前【史】</note><app n="0009001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【原】">葥</rdg></app>建德郡<note n="0009002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">承＝丞【史】</note><app n="0009002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">丞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">承</rdg></app>沃連戍軍主呂安辰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a03"/>夫至道無名。故顯名以為真。玄<note n="0009003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30347;＝寂【史】</note><app n="0009003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30347;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a04"/>難辯。假<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">幻</unclear>象以明壞。是以如來□道
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a05"/>以濟萬類。大推隨方而拔群溺。□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a06"/>更<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">陶</unclear>□造。品物<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">咸</unclear>享者也。斯寔□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a07"/>之典。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">御</unclear>九聖之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">師</unclear>光。自<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">非</unclear>刊石荊山。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a08"/>真容將來□蠹□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">嗟</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">恤</unclear>於是与
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a09"/>沃<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">黎</unclear>戍軍主呂安辰。隊主劉都〃。劉
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a10"/>初丹。張惠初。劉胡堤等七十四人。□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a11"/>趣<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">府</unclear><note n="0009004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01002;＝&CB00515;【史】</note><app n="0009004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">&CB00515;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01002;</rdg></app>三途。覬一豪之善。有所因感
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a12"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">於</unclear>夷方之右。沃黎之西。建造私窟。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a13"/>是以暉聖容且表微塵之心耳。□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a14"/>來因果。上鐘景明。下及&CB00311;虫<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">不</unclear>□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a15"/>無二。聊記年月也。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a16"/>玄樞至妙。太虛檄文。檄陳□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">範</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a17"/>悟<note n="0009005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13426;＝海【史】</note><app n="0009005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13426;</rdg></app>淪滅<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">空</unclear>明<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">定</unclear>象法敷□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a18"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">濟</unclear>□生集為珍
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a19"/>大魏景明三年五月九日造。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a20"/>尉劉□丹使員外散騎常侍昌黎韓貞。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a21"/>前建德郡<app source="0009002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">丞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">承</rdg></app>沃<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">黎</unclear>戍軍主呂安辰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a22"/>尉喻使令史□國淳于敬□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a23"/>　　隊主劉都〃
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a24"/>　　隊主張惠初
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a25"/>　　隊主劉初丹
<lb ed="C I" n="0009a26"/>　　賢者劉護堤</p>
